query:
SELECT
            id as "id!",
            is_video as "is_video!",
            use_panorama_viewer as "is_panorama!",
            duration_ms::INT,
            taken_at_local::TEXT as "timestamp!"
        FROM
            media_item
        WHERE
            user_id = $1
            AND deleted = false
            AND month_id = ANY($2)
        ORDER BY
            sort_timestamp DESC
